\c 8
\s Vana vaBhenjamini naSauro
\p
\v 1 Zvino Bhenjamini wakabereka Bhera dangwe rake, Ashibheri wepiri, naAhara wetatu,
\v 2 Noha wechina, naRafa weshanu.
\v 3 Uye Bhera waiva nevanakomana: Adhari, naGera, naAbhihudhi,
\v 4 naAbhishuwa, naNaamani, naAhowa,
\v 5 naGera, naShefufani, naHuramu.
\v 6 Zvino ava vanakomana vaEhudhi: Ndivo misoro yemadzibaba evagari vepaGebha, uye vakavatapira kuManahati;
\v 7 naNaamani, naAhiya, naGera, iye wakavatapa; ndokubereka Uza naAhihudhi.
\v 8 Shaharaimu ndokubereka panyika yaMoabhu, shure kwekuvadzinga kwake. Hushimi naBhahara vaiva vakadzi vake.
\v 9 Zvino wakabereka kumukadzi wake Hodheshi: Jobhabhu, naZibhia, naMesha, naMarikamu,
\v 10 naJeuzi, naSakiya, naMirima. Ava vanakomana vake, misoro yemadzibaba.
\v 11 Zvino kuna Hushimi wakabereka Abhitubhi naEripahari.
\v 12 Uye vanakomana vaEripahari: Ebheri, naMishamu, naShemedhi; iye wakavaka Ono, neRodhi, nemisha yawo,
\v 13 naBheriya, naShema; ivo vaiva misoro yemadzibaba kuvagari vepaAjaroni; ivo vaiva vadzinga vagari vepaGati;
\v 14 naAhiyo, Shashaki, naJeremoti,
\v 15 naZebhadhia, naAradhi, naEdheri,
\v 16 naMikayeri, naIshipa, naJoha, vanakomana vaBheriya;
\v 17 naZebhadhia, naMeshuramu, naHiziki, naHebheri,
\v 18 naIshimerai, naIziriya, naJobhabhu, vanakomana vaEripahari;
\v 19 naJakimu, naZikiri, naZabhudhi,
\v 20 naErienai, naZiretai, naEriyeri,
\v 21 naAdhaya, naBheraya, naShimurati, vanakomana vaShimei;
\v 22 naIshipani, naEbheri, naEriyeri,
\v 23 naAbhudhoni, naZikiri, naHanani,
\v 24 naHananiya, naEramu, naAnitotiya,
\v 25 naIfudheya, naPenueri, vanakomana vaShashaki;
\v 26 naShamusherai, naShehariya, naAtariya,
\v 27 naJaareshiya, naEriya, naZikiri, vanakomana vaJerohamu.
\v 28 Ava vaiva misoro yemadzibaba, misoro pamadzinza avo; ava vaigara muJerusarema.
\p
\v 29 NepaGibhiyoni paigara baba vaGibhiyoni; nezita remukadzi wake raiva Mahaka;
\v 30 uye mwanakomana wake dangwe aiva Abhidhoni; naZuri, naKishi, naBhahari, naNadhabhi,
\v 31 naGedhori, naAhiyo, naZekeri.
\v 32 Mikiroti ndokubereka Shimeya. Uye avawo vaigara pakatarisana nehama dzavo muJerusarema, pamwe nehama dzavo.
\p
\v 33 Neri ndokubereka Kishi, Kishi ndokubereka Sauro, Sauro ndokubereka Jonatani, naMariki-Shua, naAbhinadhabhu, naEshibhaari.
\v 34 Zvino mwanakomana waJonatani waiva Meribhi-Bhaari; Meribhi-Bhaari ndokubereka Mika.
\v 35 Nevanakomana vaMika: Pitoni, naMereki, naTareya, naAhazi.
\v 36 Ahazi ndokubereka Jehoadha, Jehoadha ndokubereka Aremeti, naAzimavheti, naZimiri; Zimiri ndokubereka Moza;
\v 37 Moza ndokubereka Bhineya; Rafa waiva mwanakomana wake, Ereasa mwanakomana wake, Azeri mwanakomana wake.
\v 38 Zvino Azeri waiva nevanakomana vatanhatu; uye awa ndiwo mazita avo: Azirikamu, Bhokeru, naIshimaeri, naShearia, naObhadhiya, naHanani. Ava vese vaiva vanakomana vaAzeri.
\v 39 Nevanakomana vaEsheki munin'ina wake: Uramu dangwe rake, Jeushi wepiri, naErifereti wetatu.
\v 40 Zvino vanakomana vaUramu vaiva varume vane simba veumhare, vaihwembura uta; vaiva nevanakomana vazhinji, nevanakomana vevanakomana, zana nemakumi mashanu. Ava vese vaiva vevanakomana vaBhenjamini.